# Firmware Management

## Firmware Directory

The [firmware/](mdc:firmware) directory contains microcontroller code for the Everwood CNC hardware:

- [firmware/microcontroller/](mdc:firmware/microcontroller): Microcontroller firmware code
- [firmware/platformio.ini](mdc:firmware/platformio.ini): PlatformIO configuration

## Firmware Setup

The firmware setup flow is handled in:
- [renderer/pages/firmware-setup.tsx](mdc:renderer/pages/firmware-setup.tsx): UI for firmware management
- [main/background.ts](mdc:main/background.ts): Contains handlers for firmware operations

## Device Communication

Device communication is managed through:
- Serial port communication using SerialPort library
- IPC handlers for communication between UI and device
